quran[13]{c,v,t,f}:
  42,32,"Ó tún wà nínú àwọn àmì Rẹ̀, àwọn ọkọ̀ ojú-omi tó ń rìn lójú omi (tó dà) bí àwọn òkè àpáta gíga.",""
  42,33,"Tí Allāhu bá fẹ́, Ó máa dá atẹ́gùn náà dúró, (àwọn ọkọ̀ ojú-omi náà) sì máa dúró pa sójú kan náà lórí omi. Dájúdájú àwọn àmì wà nínú ìyẹn fún gbogbo onísùúrù, olùdúpẹ́.",""
  42,34,"Tàbí kí Ó kó ìparun bá (àwọn ọkọ̀ ojú-omi náà) nítorí ohun tí àwọn èrò ọkọ̀ ojú-omi ṣe (níṣẹ́ aburú). Ó sì ń ṣàmójúkúrò níbi ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀.",""
  42,35,"Àwọn tó ń (fi irọ́) ja àwọn āyah Wa ní iyàn sì máa mọ̀ pé kò sí ibùsásí kan fún wọn.",""
  42,36,"Nítorí náà, ohunkóhun tí A bá fún yín, ìgbádùn ayé nìkan ni. Ohun tí ó wà lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu lóore jùlọ, ó sì máa ṣẹ́kù títí láéláé fún àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ń gbáralé Olúwa wọn.",""
  42,37,"(Ohun tí ó wà lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu tún wà fún) àwọn tó ń jìnnà sí àwọn ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ ńlá ńlá àti àwọn ìwà ìbàjẹ́, àti (àwọn tó jẹ́ pé) nígbà tí wọ́n bá bínú, wọn yóò ṣàforíjìn.",""
  42,38,"(Ohun tí ó wà lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu tún wà fún) àwọn tó jẹ́pè ti Olúwa wọn, tí wọ́n ń kírun, ọ̀rọ̀ ara wọn sì jẹ́ ìjíròrò láààrin ara wọn, wọ́n tún ń ná nínú arísìkí tí A pèsè fún wọn.",""
  42,39,"(Ohun tí ó wà lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu tún wà fún) àwọn tí (ó jẹ́ pé) nígbà tí wọ́n bá ṣe àbòsí sí wọn, wọn yóò gbẹ̀san wọn padà.",""
  42,40,"Ẹ̀san aburú sì ni aburú bí irú rẹ̀.<sup>1</sup> Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì ṣàmójúkúrò, tí ó tún ṣàtúnṣe, ẹ̀san rẹ̀ wà lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu. Dájúdájú (Allāhu) kò nífẹ̀ẹ́ àwọn alábòsí.","[1] Kíyè sí i, gbólóhùn yìí “Ẹ̀san aburú sì ni aburú bí irú rẹ̀.” kò tako sūrah Fussilat; 41:31. Ìdí ni pé, gbígba ẹ̀san lára alábòsí tàbí gbígba ààrọ̀ kò sọ pé mùsùlùmí kò ní ẹ̀mí àforíjìn, àmọ́ ó lè má nìí agbára láti ṣàmójú kúrò fún alábòsí náà. Bí àpẹ̀ẹrẹ, kí ẹnì kan ba dúkìá mùsùlùmí jẹ́, yálà ó ṣèèsì tàbí ó mọ̀ọ́mọ̀, mùsùlùmí lè gbẹ̀san ààrọ̀ níwọ̀n ìgbà tí agbára rẹ̀ kò bá gbé àtúnṣe rẹ̀ tàbí ìràpadà rẹ̀. Kò sì níí gbà ju ohun tí wọ́n bàjẹ́."
  42,41,"Dájúdájú ẹni tí ó bá sì gbẹ̀san lẹ́yìn tí wọ́n ṣe àbòsí sí i, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn (tí wọ́n ṣàbòsí sí), kò sí ìbáwí kan kan fún wọn.",""
  42,42,"Àwọn tí ìbáwí wà fún ni àwọn tó ń ṣàbòsí sí àwọn ènìyàn, tí wọ́n tún ń tayọ ẹnu-ààlà lórí ilẹ̀ láì lẹ́tọ̀ọ́. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro wà fún.",""
  42,43,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ṣe sùúrù, tí ó tún ṣàforíjìn, dájúdájú ìyẹn wà nínú àwọn ìpinnu ọ̀rọ̀.",""
  42,44,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí Allāhu bá ṣì lọ́nà, kò tún sí aláàbò kan fún un mọ́ lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀. O sì máa rí àwọn alábòsí nígbà tí wọ́n bá rí Iná, wọn yóò wí pé: “Ǹjẹ́ ọ̀nà kan kan wà tí a lè fi padà sí ilé ayé?”",""
